ent-STWeaponShotgunSawedOf = Sawed-off TOZ-34
    .desc = Soviet double-barreled shotgun with vertical barrel arrangement. Prized in the Zone for its reliability and powerful stopping effect against mutants. Sawed-off version.
ent-STWeaponShotgunSawedOfAnomaly = Anomalous Sawed-off TOZ-34
    .desc = Anomaly-tainted sawed-off TOZ-34. Barrels glow faintly and capacity defies physics. 'The Zone loves to distort even simple weapons'.